holland-lvm
===========

This package provides an API to access Logical Volume Managemer (LVM) objects.

The current modules in holland.lib.lvm as of this writing are:

* holland.lvm.command  - Low-level API that accesses LVM commands directly
* holland.lvm.base     - Base object classes to access LVM volumes through
                             an object-oriented API
* holland.lvm.snapshot - Snapshot support to walk through the lifecycle of
                             a standard LVM snapshot and perform pluggable 
                             callback actions at each step
* holland.lvm.util     - Utility methods used by holland.lvm
